9. Another example

sentence = "Mark and John are working at Google."
print(nltk.ne_chunk(nltk.pos_tag(nltk.word_tokenize(sentence))))
#Mark/NNP is a level-2 leaf, part of a PERSON chunk. and/CC is a level-1 leaf, meaning itâ€™s not part of any chunk.

